INSERT INTO `product` VALUES (1,'2024-11-26','Shampoo','<p>Sulfate-free shampoo for color-treated hair to help prolong salon professional haircolor and deliver intense shine.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>THE BENEFITS</h2><p>The latest innovation in color care, Redken\'s Acidic Color Gloss Shampoo is a revolutionary shampoo that extends color and provides salon-like shine. This sulfate-free shampoo provides long-lasting color vibrancy for up to 32 washes* and locks in intense molecular-level shine for up to 76% shinier hair**. The acidic pH formula with amino acids and vitamin E help seal the cuticle and lock in shine to protect color from fading and dulling that may be caused by water and heat. Use as a complete routine with Acidic Color Gloss Activated Glass Gloss Treatment, Conditioner and Heat Protection Leave-In Treatment.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>KEY BENEFITS:</h3><ul><li>Color vibrancy for up to 32 washes*</li><li>Acidic pH formulas seal cuticle + lock in shine​</li><li>Sulfate-free cleansing​</li><li>Hair looks &amp; feels revitalized instantly ​</li><li>Color protection &amp; salon-grade shine for colored &amp; glossed hair​</li></ul>','redken.jpg','Redken Acidic Color Gloss Shampoo 33.8oz / 1000ml',58.95,500,'Active'),(2,'2024-11-26','Shampoo','<ul><li>Pureology Hydrate Conditioner, 8.5 oz Pack of 2</li><li>Intensely hydrate without weighing hair</li><li>For concentrated natural conditioning</li><li>Awakens the senses with an energizing, refreshing fragrance</li><li>Replenishes parched hair with movement and manageability</li><li>Rehydrates lightened and chemically relaxed hair</li></ul><p>A lavish concentrated hydrating daily conditioner Contains an exclusive AntiFadeComplex that maximizes color retention Delivers intense moisture without weighing hair down Provides concentrated natural conditioning while reducing static Replenishes parched hair with movement &amp; manageability Infused with a refreshing fragrance that awakens the senses Hair appears suppler sleeker &amp; shiner in vibrant color Perfect for dry color-treated hair.&nbsp;Pureology Hydrate Condition reveals soft, lustrous hair while protecting color vibrancy with this luxurious, concentrated daily hydrating conditioner. The exclusive AntiFadeComplex maximizes color retention.</p>','pureology.jpg','Pureology Hydrate Duo Set - Shampoo and Conditioner 8.5 oz',59.99,500,'Active'),(3,'2024-11-26','Shampoo','<h3><strong>KERASTASE DISCIPLINE BAIN FLUIDEALISTE</strong><br>Smooth-in Motion Shampoo</h3><p><strong>Kerastase Discipline Bain Fluidealiste</strong>&nbsp;is designed for thick, unruly hair to protect against frizz and humidity for up to 72 hours. This shampoo is more than just a simple cleanser, it will gently cleanse away impurities without weighing down the hair, whilst the pro-keratin formula restores and re-establishes the integrity of the hair structure.<br><strong>Kerastase Discipline Bain Fluidealiste</strong>&nbsp;is enriched with amino acids, a wheat protein derivative, and ceramide R, which smooths and strengthens the hair and creates an even surface and a hydrophobic layer that protects the hair from humidity. Your hair will be left with natural movement, a soft texture, and a frizz-free finish.</p><p><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul><li>Perfect for thick, unruly, fairly sensitized or chemically treated hair types</li><li>Gently cleanses impurities</li><li>Does not weigh the hair down</li><li>Delivers 72 hours anti frizz protection</li><li>Restores the integrity of the hair</li><li>Cruelty-free/No Animal Testing</li></ul><p><strong>Usage:</strong></p><p>Apply a quarter-sized amount to wet hair. Massage throughout and lather. Rinse thoroughly. For Ultimate results follow with Kerastase Maskeratine Masque or Kerastase Fondant Fluidealiste.</p>','kerastase.jpg','KERASTASE Discipline Bain Fluidealiste 1000ml, Anti Frizz Smoothing Shampoo',84,500,'Active'),(4,'2024-11-26','Conditioner','<ul><li>Apple Cider Vinegar Shampoo for Itchy Scalp and Product Build Up - Finally, a Detox that doesn’t suck. Get rid of product and hard water buildup, dirt and oil with this 1-2x week clarifying shampoo. Here\'s your fresh start, see you next week.</li><li>Time to Detox - This cleansing shampoo uses chelating agents to help remove heavy metals, minerals, and chlorine found in hard water, which can cause color fading to the hair while apple cider vinegar exfoliates, removing flakes and build-up to restore volume, bounce, and shine.</li><li>OUAI Means Yes - In that casual Parisian way. OUAI is about being better IRL. It\'s about having honest conversations with our community. It\'s about letting go of unrealistic expectations and embracing your imperfections.</li><li>Made For Effortless Routines - All OUAI hair care products including this sulfate-free shampoo are carefully crafted to cut styling time and nourish your hair health. We put the good stuff in and leave the bad stuff out, without ever sacrificing quality.</li><li>Live Life Your OUAI - OUAI offers luxury hair products at affordable prices that are user-friendly — no glam squad needed. Wet your hair, lather up with ACV shampoo and rinse clean. Follow with any OUAI conditioner to soften your squeaky clean strands.</li></ul>','ouai.jpg','OUAI Detox Shampoo - Clarifying Shampoo Sulfate-Free Hair Care (10 oz)',25,500,'Active'),(5,'2024-11-26','Conditioner','<h2><strong>Oud Royal Forever Shine Conditioner with MegaBounce</strong></h2><h2><strong>Philip B Oud Royal Forever Shine Conditioner with MegaBounce</strong></h2><p>The first-ever time-released conditioner for mega-bounce and shine that go on for days.</p><ul><li>A truly new technology: Moisturizing botanicals are treated with high-vapor energy, breaking them into tiny molecules that sink in and strengthen hair from the inside out</li><li>Transforms all hair types with instant, dramatic results: Revives, defines and de-frizzes curls; creates sleek, swingy blowouts; and lends fine hair uplifting body and fullness.</li><li>A time-released botanical delivery system (made with natural Safflower Oleosomes) infuses hair with lasting glossiness, bounce, and the light, seductive scent of pure Oud</li><li>Paraben free; color &amp; keratin-treatment safe</li></ul>','philip.jpg','Oud Royal Forever Shine Conditioner with MegaBounce',98,500,'Active'),(6,'2024-11-26','Conditioner','<h3>94% NATURAL INGREDIENTS<br>GLUTEN FREE AND VEGAN</h3><p>Naturally quench your thirsty, weakened tresses with our luxurious detangling and color-protecting conditioner. Crème de Soin à l’Amarante is enriched with botanical extracts for shine, hydration, color protection, and ultra frizz prevention. Includes protein-packed amaranth, vitamin-rich jojoba oil and protective karanja oil. This award-winner is named for the beautifully-scented amaranth flower, treasured for its long-lasting hue and strength.</p>','leonor.jpg','Crème de Soin à l’Amarante Detangling and Color-Protecting Conditioner',58.5,500,'Active'),(7,'2024-11-26','Hair Oil n Serum','<h3>Oribe Gold Lust All Over Oil Hair, Body, Face 50ml 1.7oz WOB</h3><p>Nourish the hair, body and face with Oribe Gold Lust All Over Oil, a hydrating and softening blend of natural oils for an all-over glow.</p><ul><li>Suitable for use all over the hair and body</li><li>Coconut oil is a rich source of fatty acids</li><li>Contains argan oil to encourage lightweight shine for the hair</li><li>Olive fruit oil helps to condition and protect the skin</li><li>Hydrates and moisturises to promote a radiant, healthy glow</li></ul>','oribe.jpg','Oribe Gold Lust All Over Oil Hair, Body, Face 50ml 1.7oz WOB NEW',39.98,500,'Active'),(8,'2024-11-26','Hair Oil n Serum','<h3>Pre-shampoo Treatment Oil for Dry Hair, Protection from the Sun and Water</h3><h4>97% NATURAL INGREDIENTS<br>GLUTEN FREE AND VEGAN</h4><p>Use this iconic pre-shampoo treatment oil for thirsty and over-processed tresses. The naturally hydrating ingredients of L’Huile de Leonor Greyl include organic jojoba, coconut, sunflower seed and sesame seed oils, which are packed with vitamins C, B and E, omegas and antioxidants. Apply L’Huile de Leonor Greyl to dry hair 10 minutes before shampooing, or leave it on overnight as an intensive weekly therapy. This oil also provides sun protection when applied before spending a day at the pool or beach.</p>','lhuile.jpg','Leonor Greyl L\'Huile de Leonor Greyl Pre-Shampoo Treatment Oil',45,500,'Active'),(9,'2024-11-26','Hair Oil n Serum','<h2><strong>Item description from the seller</strong></h2><ul><li>The Precious Hair Care Oil provides nutrition, radiance and softness to the hair</li><li>It has a light texture that will not weigh down your hair and is delicately scented.</li><li>Smoothed and nourished, the hair is immediately enhanced</li><li>The oil rapidly smooths and nourishes each strand, resulting in lustrous locks.</li><li>It contains Shea oil, which moisturizes and smooths the cuticle, as well as moringa oil, which preserves the strands</li></ul>','sisley.jpg','Sisley Hair Rituel Precious Hair Care Oil 3.3oz/100ml',72.97,500,'Active'),(10,'2024-11-26','Foundation','<h2><strong>Item description from the seller</strong><br>&nbsp;</h2><p>What It Is:</p><p>A long wear foundation infused with Hyaluronic Acid and light-diffusing microspheres for a blurring effect and a skin-like matte finish. 40 shades.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>What else you should know:</p><ul><li>Hydrating. Longwear. Medium-Full coverage.</li><li>Defy Conventions: Traceless Soft Matte Foundation is matte without looking flat, cakey, or dry. It combines soft-focus microsphere powders that blur imperfections with wear-extending pigments that provide medium to full buildable coverage. The soft and silky texture is ultra-blendable and defends against caking, poring and settling. Skin still looks and moves like skin and feels smoother over time, even after foundation has been removed.</li><li>Hydration and Longwear: This high-performance formula is formulated with hyaluronic acid to help support skin\'s moisture barrier and antioxidants, Vitamin C &amp; E and caffeine. Treat your complexion to all day, ultra-comfortable long wear.</li><li>Tom Ford\'s Definition of a Modern Matte Finish Foundation: 40 color-true shades for a traceless, soft-focus finish that looks and feels natural and flawless.</li></ul><blockquote><p>\"Looking through a camera lens has taught me that an even skin tone and texture is very important. A perfected matte look is beautiful, but should not look flat or dry. Above all it must move like skin.\" - Tom Ford</p></blockquote>','tomford.jpg','TOM FORD Traceless Soft Matte Foundation 10.7 AMBER 1 oz / 30 ml New in Box',45.99,499,'Active'),(11,'2024-11-26','Foundation','<h2><strong>Item description from the seller</strong></h2><p>Giorgio Armani Luminous Silk Foundation is a multi-award-winning liquid foundation with a silky, lightweight texture that delivers all-day buildable medium coverage with a satin glow finish for naturally flawless-looking skin and a no-makeup makeup look. This oil-free foundation is formulated with exclusive Micro–fil &amp; trade technology, a patented process that allows the pigments to lay flat on the skin’s surface for a seamless application and a natural, second-skin effect.<br><br><strong>Benefits:</strong><br>Medium buildable coverage<br>Naturally luminous, airbrushed finish<br>Oil-free<br>For all skin types</p>','armani.jpg','Giorgio Armani Luminous Silk Foundation #9 Tan to Deep 30ml/1oz – NEW',39.99,500,'Active'),(12,'2024-11-26','Foundation','<h3><strong>Cle De Peau Beaute Radiant Fluid Foundation Broad Spectrum SPF 24 (O60) Very Deep Ochre 1fl.oz/30ml - NEW BOX - Free USA Shipping</strong></h3><p><strong>A liquid foundation that gives skin a dewy lustrous finish and creates a glowing veil of beauty. Emits multi-dimensional light from the surface of the complexion to provide an even radiance and a fine texture. Protects skin with broad spectrum SPF 24.</strong></p><h2><strong>Key Benefits</strong></h2><ul><li>Contains Illuminating Complex, a powerful moisture-stabilizing force that promotes exquisite radiance.</li><li>Day Matching Powder responds to changes in skin tone throughout the day and maintains a perfect foundation finish.</li><li>Watery Oil Base provides a uniquely dewy, lustrous finish.</li><li>Imparts a “glowing veil” to reveal a vibrant luminosity that transcends the natural look of skin.</li><li>Resists dullness, wear and changes in color throughout the day to retain a beautiful finish for hours.</li><li>Moisturizes skin and allows you to feel hydrating treatment.</li><li>Developed with a dewy serum-like texture that glides on as if melting over skin to become one with your complexion and provide a smooth finish.</li><li>Contains Chestnut Rose Fruit Extract to make skin feel soft providing moisture while preventing skin from looking dull.</li></ul>','clede.jpg','Cle De Peau Beaute Radiant Fluid Foundation SPF 24 (O60) Very Deep Ochre 30ml US',120,497,'Active'),(13,'2024-11-26','Concealer','<p>What It Is:<br>Natural, buildable and weightless coverage, under-eye brightening, dark-circle correcting, skin-loving brush concealer.<br><br>What It Does:<br>The Touche Éclat High Cover Radiant Concealer erases hereditary dark circles, helps to erase signs of fatigue, and corrects the all over eye area. The entire eye instantly looks awake and bright. Higher coverage than the original Touche Éclat, this formula is buildable for as much coverage as needed. It is the ultimate no-makeup makeup formula: create flawless coverage without ever looking overdone or artificial. The built-in brush applicator is perfect for applying and blending in the small eye area.<br><br>Key Ingredients:</p><ul><li>Caffeine + Ruscus Extract: under-eye puffiness and swelling</li><li>Hyaluronic Acid: hydrates</li><li>Vitamin E + Calendula Extract: antioxidant-rich and soothing to protect and care for delicate eye area</li></ul><p>Formulated Without:</p><ul><li>Pthalate-Free</li><li>Sulfate-Free</li><li>Paraben-Free</li></ul>','ysl.png','YSL Touche Eclat High Cover Radiant Concealer #1.5 Beige Full Sz .08oz NIB',39.99,489,'Active'),(14,'2024-11-26','Concealer','<p>Brand new in box Magic Away Concealer from Charlotte Tilbury.<br>Shade: 14 Deep (a warm bronze shade for deep skin tones with peach undertones).<br>Reduces the appearance of dark circles, blemishes and imperfections<br>Cushion applicator designed to hug the under eye contour.<br>Size: 4ml</p>','charlotte.jpg','Charlotte Tilbury Magic Away Liquid Concealer 14 Deep NEW',24.99,500,'Active'),(15,'2024-11-26','Concealer','<p>Tarte Shape Tape Full Coverage Contour Concealer&nbsp;- 0.3381oz - <strong>Shade 12S&nbsp;Fair -</strong> 12S is for fair skin with yellow undertones.&nbsp; This incredible best selling concealer is a vegan, super blendable formula that instantly helps brighten, smooth and give skin a firmer, more lifted look. Full coverage with flawless matte finish. Conceals all imperfections and doubles as a contour/highlight product. Creamy, easy to blend formula won\'t flake or crease. Helps illuminate skin for a lifted effect. Shea Butter is a natural skin emollient that helps retain skin elasticity and protects against degeneration. Mango Seed Butter is a vitamin rich butter that helps moisturize, condition and protect against free radical damage. Licorice Root Extract brightens the appearance of dark circles and color corrects. Always formulated without parabens, mineral oil, phthalates, triclosan, sodium lauryl sulfate, and gluten. Vegan, dermatologist tested, cruelty free.</p>','tarte.jpg','Tarte Shape Tape Full Coverage Contour Concealer Shade 12S Fair',26,500,'Active'),(16,'2024-11-26','Eyeliner','<p>Lancome ARTLINER 24H Eyeliner Bold Color Precision Eye Liner&nbsp;</p><p>Shade: 01 BLACK DIAMOND (black)</p><p>Suitable for sensitive eyes</p><p>Shake before use</p><p>Discontinued and very hard to find</p>','lancome.jpg','Lancome Artliner 24H Eyeliner Bold Color Precision Eye Liner 1 BLACK DIAMOND',46.7,498,'Active'),(17,'2024-11-26','Eyeliner','<p>Marc Jacobs Highliner Gel Eye Crayon In Fine (Wine) *Brand New*.</p><p>This beautiful eyeliner from Marc Jacobs can be paired with your favorite eyeshadows or worn alone.</p><p>The texture is creamy and glides onto the eyes.</p><p>The eyeliner won’t smudge and is long lasting.</p><p>This item is authentic.</p>','marc.jpg','Marc Jacobs Highliner Gel Eye Crayon In Fine (Wine) *Brand New*',44,500,'Active'),(18,'2024-11-26','Eyeliner','<p>NEW Stila Stay All Day Waterproof Liquid Eye Liner Intense Black</p><p>New in box.</p><p>#1 selling liquid eye liner in an amazing, satin finish.</p><p>Fine marker-like tip offers precise application for everyone from novices to pros.</p><p>Results in beautifully defined eyes that leave a lasting impression.</p><p>Perfect to draw thin, precise lines or thick, dramatic strokes.</p><p>Waterproof, transfer-proof, and smudge-proof.</p><p>Glides on with ease, dries quickly, and won\'t smudge or run day-into-night.</p><p>Lasts all day long!</p><p>Long-wearing with no feathering or running.</p><p>Ophthalmologist tested - safe for sensitive eyes and contact lens wearers.</p>','stila.jpg','NEW Stila Stay All Day Waterproof Liquid Eye Liner Intense Black',22,500,'Active'),(19,'2024-11-26','Mascara','<h3>Description</h3><p>The Super Slim Waterproof Mascara elevates each eyelash and maintains curled lashes for an extended period</p><p>Its waterproof formula is highly resistant to water and oil, preventing makeup from smudging</p><p>This mascara aids in achieving well-defined and distinct eyelashes</p><h3>&nbsp;</h3><h3>Main Ingredients</h3><p>Isododecane, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Microcrystalline Wax, Polyethylene, Disteardimonium Hectorite, Dextrin Palmitate/Ethylhexanoate, Iron Oxide Black (CI 77499), Silica, Hydrogenated Polyisobutene, Silica Silylate, VP/Eicosene Copolymer, Polypropylsilsesquioxane, Ethylene/Propylene Copolymer, Propylene Carbonate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Sorbitan Isostearate, Polymethylsilsesquioxane, Triethoxycaprylylsilane</p><h3>&nbsp;</h3><h3>How to use</h3><p>Take an appropriate amount on the brush and gently sweep the eyelashes from bottom to top</p>','mascara.jpg','Mascara 3CE Slim Fix Waterproof 6.5g',26,500,'Active'),(20,'2024-11-26','Mascara','<p><strong>What it is:&nbsp;</strong>A mini universal mascara with a unique eye-hugging brush to lift, lengthen, curl, and volumize every lash type for a lusher look.<br><br><strong>Formulation Type:&nbsp;</strong>Volumizing, Curling, and Lengthening<br><br><strong>Benefits:&nbsp;</strong>Long-wearing<br><br><strong>Highlighted Ingredients:</strong><br>- Castor Oil: Conditions, softens, and nourishes lashes.<br><br><strong>Ingredient Callouts:</strong>&nbsp;Free of parabens. It is also vegan and cruelty-free.<br><br><strong>What Else You Need to Know:</strong>&nbsp;Finding the perfect mascara comes down to your lash type, which differs from person to person. This weightless, easy-to-build formula and curvy, multi-length brush are made to give every lash type (fine/sparse, full/thick, straight, and curly) more lift, length, curl, and volume.<br><br><strong>Clinical Results:</strong>&nbsp;In an independent instrumental study of 120 subjects:<br>- 100% of all lash types had more length and volume<br>- 95% of all lash types had more lift<br>- 92% of all lash types had more curl</p>','rarebeautymascara.jpg','3X Rare Beauty Selena Gomez Perfect Strokes Volumiz Mascara BLK .27oz MINI Trial',70,499,'Active'),(21,'2024-11-26','Mascara','<p>Instantly create the look of lash extensions with this award-winning, best-selling tubing mascara that won\'t clump, flake or smudge. This sweat-proof, water-resistant formula is available in 5 shades!</p><p><strong>Indulge in our Limited Edition packaging mascara—same iconic formula, now in an exclusive design, available for a limited time!</strong></p>','thrivemascara.jpg','Thrive Causemetics Liquid Lash Extensions Mascara',26,500,'Active'),(22,'2024-12-02','Toner','<h2>Dear, Klairs, Supple Preparation Unscented Toner, 6.08 fl oz (180 ml)</h2><h3>DESCRIPTION:</h3><p>Moisturizing Skin Care Program Essential Oil-Free Balances pH Level Deep Moisturizing Vegan Friendly Supple Preparation Unscented Toner is an essential oil-free type toner. It is formulated with a base of various botanical extracts to balance the skin\'s pH level and provide full nourishment to the skin. Our Philosophy Simple, but enough Dear, Klairs believes in \'Simple Skincare\': we use a minimal number of products catered to your exact skin type produce the best results. Basics for sensitive skin Deep Moisturizing Cleanses &amp; Soothes Balances pH Level Natural &amp; Botanical Extracts</p><h3>SUGGESTED USE:</h3><p>Apply on a clean face. Gently pat all over your face using your palms. Pat remaining product into skin until fully absorbed.</p><h3>INGREDIENTS:</h3><p>Water, butylene glycol, dimethyl sulfone, betaine, caprylic/ capric triglyceride, disodium edta, glycyrrhiza glabra (licorice) root extract, centella asiatica extract, chlorphenesin, tocopheryl acetate, glycerin, arginine, carbomer, panthenol, luffa cylindrica fruit/leaf/stem extract, 1,2-hexanediol, hydroxyethylcellulose, aloe barbadensis leaf extract, althaea rosea flower extract, portulaca oleracea extract, polyquaternium-51, beta-glucan, lysine hcl, sodium ascorbyl phosphate, sodium hyaluronate, acetyl methionine, theanine, proline, natto gum, disodium phosphate, polysorbate 60, sodium phosphate, copper tripeptide-1</p><h3>WARNINGS:</h3><p>For external use only. Discontinue use if irritation develops or increases. If irritation persists, consult a doctor or a health care practitioner. Avoid contact with eyes. Keep out of reach of children. Store in a cool, dry place away from sunlight.</p>','toner.jpg','Dear, Klairs, Supple Preparation Unscented Toner, 6.08 fl oz, Balances pH Level',21.51,498,'Active'),(23,'2024-12-02','Toner','<figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><h4>Kind to skin</h4><p>Simple Kind to Skin Soothing Facial Toner removes alkaline residue left after cleansing, helping restore the balance of your skin\'s natural pH level. Skin is toned, refreshed and ready for moisturiser.</p></td><td><h4>Skin-loving ingredients</h4><p>Our alcohol-free toner features a special blend of Simple skin-toning goodness including ingredients like pro-vitamin B5, witch hazel, chamomile and allantoin to help replenish skin\'s building blocks with every use.</p></td><td><h4>No harsh chemicals</h4><p>Simple products contain no artificial colours, perfumes or harsh chemicals that can upset skin. The non-comedogenic formula is dermatologically tested and suitable even for sensitive skin.</p></td><td><h4>Cruelty-free and vegan</h4><p>Simple Kind to Skin Soothing Toner is suitable for vegans and Simple is certified cruelty-free by PETA. We do not test on animals anywhere in the world.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><br>&nbsp;</p>','simple.jpg','Simple Kind to Skin Soothing Facial Toner 200ml | Free Shipping',3.49,497,'Active'),(24,'2024-12-02','Lipstick','<h2>Dior Rouge Dior Forever Lipstick 647 Forever Feminine</h2><p>Experience the universally flattering shade of Dior Rouge Dior Forever Lipstick in shade 647, \"Forever Feminine.\" This versatile color beautifully complements a wide range of skin tones, making it suitable for all. The long-lasting formula ensures that the color stays vibrant and intact throughout the day, providing a reliable and long-wearing option. It offers a soft, natural-looking finish with a subtle sheen that enhances the lips\\\' natural texture, creating a truly mesmerizing effect. Infused with moisturizing ingredients, this lipstick keeps the lips feeling soft and hydrated, ensuring comfort and preventing any dryness. Embrace the elegance and versatility of Dior Rouge Dior Forever Lipstick in shade 647, \"Forever Feminine.\" for a timeless and sophisticated lip look.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Universally flattering shade: The Dior Rouge Dior Forever Lipstick in shade 647, \"Forever Feminine.\" is a versatile color that complements a wide range of skin tones, making it suitable for everyone.</li><li>Long-lasting formula: This lipstick offers long-lasting wear, ensuring that the color stays vibrant and intact throughout the day.</li><li>Soft, natural-looking finish: The formula provides a soft, natural-looking finish on the lips, enhancing their natural texture and creating a subtle sheen.</li><li>Hydrating and moisturizing: Infused with moisturizing ingredients, this lipstick keeps the lips feeling soft and hydrated, preventing any dryness or discomfort.</li><li>Perfect for everyday wear: The \"Forever Feminine.\" shade is ideal for everyday wear, adding a touch of elegance and sophistication to any makeup look.</li></ul>','lipstick.jpg','Dior Rouge Dior Forever Lipstick 647 Forever Feminine',21.97,496,'Active'),(25,'2024-12-03','Lip Balm','<p>Dr. Bronner\'s Organic Lip Balms, made with organic beeswax, provide a protective barrier to the elements with no synthetic ingredients! None! Organic jojoba, avocado and hemp oils help with extra moisturization. Only the finest essential oils are used for fragrance. Certified organic to USDA National Organic Program standards, because what you put on your lips goes into your body. Vegetarian.<br><br><br><strong>SUGGESTED USES</strong><br>Use to moisturise-heal chapped-dry skin anywhere on your body! Quickly treat dry hands or cuticles, chapped chins or cheeks &amp; provide relief for chaffed skin where needed. Heal recently tattooed skin and brighten up old tattoos! For tattoo care, wash your tattoo with one of our soaps, pat the area dry and apply a thin layer of Organic Body Balm over the tattoo<br><br><br><strong>INGREDIENTS</strong><br>Organic Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil*, Organic Beeswax, Organic Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Organic Cannabis Sativa (Hemp) Seed Oil, Organic Mentha Piperita (Peppermint) Oil, Tocopherol<br>*CERTIFIED FAIR TRADE INGREDIENTS</p>','bronner.jpg','Dr Bronner\'s Peppermint Lip Balm 4g',7.75,500,'Active'),(26,'2024-12-03','Cleanser','<p><strong>What it is</strong></p><p>An antioxidant cleanser that doesn’t mess up your skin barrier, lifting everything your skin doesn\'t want while leaving what it needs; healthy pH, hydration, antioxidants and no irritation. Matcha and hemp seeds are here to boost the skin’s intake of antioxidants and essential fatty acids. Your skin and this cleanser might be a matcha made in heaven!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Capacity</strong></p><p>120ml</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Key ingredients</strong></p><p>Matcha</p><p>One of the most antioxidant-dense sources on the planet.</p><p>Basically, we thought it’d be awesome to splash matcha every day on our skin.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>Hemp seed oil</p><p>HIGH in essential amino acids, HIGH in linoleic acid, oh yeah, it’s so HIGH-drating!</p><p>Great for all skin types, even for oily skin peeps.</p><p>Hemp seed oil has a natural antibacterial property that helps to relieve inflamed skin conditions.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Coco -betaine, Coco-glucoside, Decyl glucoside</p><p>A group of mild and gentle cleaning agents.</p><p>These surfactants are less likely to compromise your skin barrier whereas harsh surfactants (like SLS) can strip away everything including your natural lipids.</p><p>And these, you don’t want to surrender.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Vitamin B5 &amp; Sodium PCA</p><p>Skin-barrier strengthening ingredients replenishing hydration.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Recommended for</strong></p><p>All skin types</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>How to use</strong></p><p>Morning and night, apply Matcha Hemp Hydrating Cleanser on a wet face and neck, and gently massage into skin. Never be aggressive! Rinse with lukewarm water. Splashing cold or hot water can do more harm than good, so let\'s not shock our skin. If makeup is present, using a suitable makeup remover before would be a skin-friendlier option.</p>','krave.jpg','[Krave Beauty] Matcha Hemp Hydrating Cleanser 120ml',24.66,489,'Active'),(27,'2024-12-03','Moisturizer','<p>Sheer Cover Advanced Nourishing Moisturizer Broad Spectrum Spf 15. 60ML SEALED.</p><p>Direction:</p><p>For best result, apply daily underneath Sheer Cover Studio Conceal and Brighten Trio and Perfect Shade Mineral Foundation.</p><p>Smooth into clean skin. Allow advanced Nourishing Moisturizer Broad Spectrum SPF 15 to absorb completely before applying makeup. May also be blended with Sheer Cover Studio. Perfect Shade Mineral Foundation to create you own tinted moisturizer.</p>','sheer.jpg','Sheer Cover Advanced Nourishing Moisturizer Broad Spectrum Spf 15',29.99,500,'Active'),(28,'2024-12-03','Serum','<h4>Description</h4><p>TNS Advanced+ Serum is clinically proven to smooth the appearance of wrinkles &amp; fine lines, target sagging, &amp; rejuvenate skin. Users felt they looked 6 years younger in just a few weeks. Reference: 1. Data on file at SkinMedica</p><h4>Benefits</h4><p>TNS Advanced+ Serum is proven to smooth the appearance of wrinkles &amp; fine lines, target sagging, &amp; rejuvenate skin.</p><h4>Suggested Use</h4><p>Dispense single pump onto the back of hand, blend together &amp; apply to face morning &amp; night. Avoid getting in eyes.</p>','skinmedica.jpg','SkinMedica TNS Advanced + Serum 1oz *New In Box* Sealed',109.99,498,'Active'),(29,'2024-12-03','Exfoliator','<p><strong>What it is:</strong><br>Helps remove dulling &amp; dead surface cells Contains Chamomilla Recutita Flower Extract &amp; Olive Leaf Extract Blended with Papaya Fruit Extract &amp; Willow Bark Extract Infused with Lactic Acid to brighten skin Stimulates cell renewal &amp; turnover Skin appears smooth, purified &amp; nourished<br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong><br>Lactic Acid, Water, Glycerin, Sodium Lactate, Hydroxypropyl Starch Phosphate, Galactoarabinan, Sodium Hydroxide, Chamomilla Recutita (Matricaria) Flower Extract, Olea Europaea (Olive) Leaf Extract, Salix Alba (Willow) Bark Extract, Protease Aminopeptidase, Bacillus Ferment, Hexanoyl Dipeptide-3 Norleucine Acetate, Lecithin, Xylitol, Cocamidopropyl PG-Dimonium Chloride Phosphate, Propylene Glycol, Ethoxydiglycol, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil.</p><p><strong>Directions:</strong><br>Apply a small amount onto face &amp; neck, massage gently. Leave on for 3 - 10 minutes. If stinging or irritation occurs, remove immediately. Remove with Dermalogica Double Cleanse that begins with PreCleanse followed by Special Cleansing Gel.</p>','dermalogica.jpg','Dermalogica Exfoliant Accelerator 35 Pro Size ( 6 fl oz / 177 mL ) Auth ',89.5,500,'Active'),(30,'2024-12-03','Sunscreen','<p><strong>Vichy Capital Soleil Mattifying Dry Touch Face Fluid SPF50</strong>&nbsp;is a&nbsp;mattifying&nbsp;face fluid with high sun protection for combination to oily skin.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Vichy Capital Soleil Mattifying Dry Touch Face Fluid SPF50</strong>&nbsp;helps to moisturize and protect oily skin, mattifying it.</p><p>- Mexoryl filters XL, UVA and UVB and Vichy thermal water for a moisturizing, protective, anti-aging, mattifying and fortifying action</p><p>- Moisturizes deeply without leaving oily skin</p><p>- Protects against solar and daily environmental aggressors</p><p>- Reinforces the skin’s natural barrier</p><p>- Prevents skin aging</p><p>- Provides high sun protection (SPF50)</p><p>- Does not block the pores</p><p>- Ideal for combination to oily skin</p><p>- No parabens</p><p>- Skin feels moisturized, soft and perfectly protected</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>HOW TO USE</strong></p><p>Apply&nbsp;<strong>Vichy Capital Soleil Mattifying Dry Touch Face Fluid SPF50</strong>&nbsp;to perfectly cleansed and dry skin, 30 minutes before sun exposure.&nbsp;Reapply the application every 2 hours or after swimming.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Vichy Capital Soleil Mattifying Dry Touch Face Fluid SPF50 50ml</strong>. Condition is New with box. Shipped with USPS First Class Package.</p>','vichy.jpg','Vichy Capital Soleil Mattifying Dry Touch Face Fluid SPF50 50ml',22.99,497,'Active'),(31,'2024-12-04','Body Lotion','<p>Reveal irresistibly soft skin with NIVEA Shea Daily Moisture Body Lotion. The lightweight, non-greasy formula in this NIVEA body lotion for dry skin intensively moisturizes for 48 hours. This moisturizing body lotion gently melts into skin leaving it silky and smooth after just one application, and is enriched with Shea Butter and NIVEA Deep Nourishing Serum. NIVEA Shea Daily Moisture Body Lotion is dermatologically tested. This shea butter moisturizer is also a perfect solution for those looking for a daily hand lotion or foot lotion. NIVEA is proud to be one of the leading companies in the field of skin care products, with more than 130 years of expertise. A daily moisturizing lotion is a key part of a skincare routine and this shea butter body lotion pairs well with NIVEA body wash as part of a daily skin care regimen. To use, smooth this nourishing shea butter lotion over dry skin.</p>','nivea.jpg','NIVEA Shea Daily Moisture Body Lotion Dry Skin Lotion w/ Shea Butter 16.9 Fl Oz',9.89,498,'Active'),(32,'2024-12-04','Deodorant','<p>We all spend plenty of time on our skin and hair care routines but it’s easy to forget about underarm care. Frankly, our underarms deserve better! Good news: you can care for your underarms every day with a quick spritz of Dove Original Antiperspirant Deodorant. It helps give you beautifully soft and smooth underarm skin, while providing up to 48 hours of antiperspirant protection.</p><p>Dove antiperspirant deodorants help to reduce the irritation on your delicate underarm skin that can be caused by shaving. They contain ¼ moisturizing cream for beautifully soft and smooth underarms. In fact, the ¼ moisturizing cream in our formula is proven to give you soft and smooth underarm skin after just three days of use.</p><p>Like all of our Dove Original products, this antiperspirant deodorant has a delicate scent that helps to keep you smelling fresh and clean all day long.</p><p>Try our Original Antiperspirant Deodorant spray for outstanding underarm care and protection against underarm wetness and odor, plus the signature Dove Original scent you know and love.</p><h2>Perfect for</h2><ul><li>Soft, smooth underarms. Our unique ¼ moisturizing cream helps to nourish and protect your delicate underarm skin so that it is even softer and smoother</li><li>&nbsp;Long-lasting protection If you want cared for, smooth underarms and freshness that lasts all day, Dove Original Antiperspirant is for you, giving you 48-hours of protection</li><li>Helping skin recover after shaving. The ¼ moisturizing cream also helps your skin to recover from the irritation that shaving can cause, so you can feel confident that your delicate underarm skin is cared for</li></ul><h2>How to use</h2><p>For the best all-day protection: after showering, make sure your underarms are completely dry (and cool, if possible). Then shake your can to evenly mix the protecting and nourishing ingredients. Finally, holding your arm above your head, spray one underarm at a time with a good spritz. Holding the can about 15cm away from underarms for about two seconds is perfect. It’s really as simple as that.</p>','dove.jpg','Dove Women 150 ML/5.07 FL OZ Antiperspirant Deodorant Spray Assortment',4,499,'Active'),(33,'2024-12-04','Hand n Foot Care','<p>Rule one in beauty is that you can own The best make up in the world, but it won\'t look good unless your skin is happy, healthy and nourished. Target your concerns and find the daily essentials that will improve your overall skin health. Tried and tested, these are the formulas that really work.</p><p>We created Compact by Design to identify products that, while they may not always look very different, have a more efficient design. With the removal of excess air and water, products require less packaging and become more efficient to dispatch. At scale, these small differences in product size and weight lead to significant carbon emission reductions.</p><p>Rule one in beauty is that you can own The best make up in the world, but it won\'t look good unless your skin is happy, healthy and nourished. Target your concerns and find the daily essentials that will improve your overall skin health. Tried and tested, these are the formulas that really work.</p><p>Vaseline soothing hand cream accelerates dry skin\'s ability to repair itself by infusing and locking in the moisture it needs. With non - greasy formulation, it leaves an invisible protective shield on hands. Hypoallergenic.</p><p>Aqua, Paraffinum Liquidum, Stearic Acid, Dimethicone, Glycerin, Glycol Stearate, Collagen Amino Acids, Cyclopentasiloxane, Dihydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Hydrolyzed Keratin, Hydrolyzed Milk Protein, Hydroxyethyl Urea, Lactic Acid</p><p>Vaseline heals all skin to make it beautifully healthy and Vaseline Intensive Care Healthy Hands Stronger Nails Hand Cream is no different. With a unique keratin formula and microdroplets of our triple-purified Vaseline jelly, this moisturising hand cream penetrates deep into the stratum corneum (outer layer) of the skin, delivering instant and deep moisture to dry hands and itchy skin.</p>','vaseline.jpg','Vaseline Intensive Care Advanced Repair Cream',11.99,495,'Active'),(34,'2024-12-23','Shampoo','<p>yen yen yen</p>','armani.jpg','yen',77,52,'Active');
